This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the interpretability of deep learning models. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as deep learning is a subfield of AI. Additionally, since the paper focuses on convolutional neural networks (CNNs), it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.CL (Computation and Language) as CNNs are commonly used in these fields. Finally, since the paper discusses the importance of establishing trust for commercial use, it could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
